# TASK-BACKLOG.md — TestBot's 40-Task Backlog
*Created: 2026-03-03 by TestBot + Stephen*
*Single source of truth for all backlog tasks across 4 tracks.*
*Status: [ ] open | [x] done | [~] in progress | [>] queued for today*

---

## How This Works
- Task-runner picks the next [ ] task per track each run
- Evening update detects no-progress tracks and queues a task
- 3-day review checks completion rate and reorders if stalled
- Never delete tasks — mark [x] when done so we can see the arc

